				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the conflict of 1919–21.  For other Russo–Polish conflicts, see <a href="Polish%E2%80%93Russian_War_(disambiguation)" title="Polish–Russian War (disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect">Polish–Russian War</a>.</div>
