</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="background-color: #DCDCDC; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Part of the <a href="Russian_Civil_War" title="Russian Civil War">Russian Civil War</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Polish-soviet_war_1920_Polish_defences_near_Milosna,_August.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Polish-soviet war 1920 Polish defences near Milosna, August.jpg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bd/Polish-soviet_war_1920_Polish_defences_near_Milosna,_August.jpg/300px-Polish-soviet_war_1920_Polish_defences_near_Milosna,_August.jpg" width="300" height="237" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bd/Polish-soviet_war_1920_Polish_defences_near_Milosna%2C_August.jpg/450px-Polish-soviet_war_1920_Polish_defences_near_Milosna%2C_August.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bd/Polish-soviet_war_1920_Polish_defences_near_Milosna%2C_August.jpg/600px-Polish-soviet_war_1920_Polish_defences_near_Milosna%2C_August.jpg 2x" /></a><br />
Polish defenses at <a href="Mi%C5%82osna,_Warmian-Masurian_Voivodeship" title="Miłosna, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship">Miłosna</a>, during the decisive <a href="Battle_of_Warsaw_(1920)" title="Battle of Warsaw (1920)">battle of Warsaw</a>, August 1920.</td>
</tr>
