<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; font-size: 110%;">Strength</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width:50%; border-right:1px dotted #aaa;">From ~50,000 in early 1919<sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> to almost 800,000 in summer 1920<sup id="cite_ref-davies_WERS_142_3-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-davies_WERS_142-3"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
<td style="width:50%; padding-left:0.25em">From ~50,000 in early 1919<sup id="cite_ref-4" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-4"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup> to ~738,000 in August 1920<sup id="cite_ref-Davies_WERS-196.3B202pl_5-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Davies_WERS-196.3B202pl-5"><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; font-size: 110%;">Casualties and losses</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width:50%; border-right:1px dotted #aaa;">estimated 60,000 killed<sup id="cite_ref-Rummel1990_6-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Rummel1990-6"><span>[</span>5<span>]</span></a></sup><br />
80,000 – 157,000 taken prisoner
<p><sup id="cite_ref-7" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-7"><span>[</span>6<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-8" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-8"><span>[</span>7<span>]</span></a></sup> (including rear-area personnel)</p>
</td>
<td style="width:50%; padding-left:0.25em">About 48,000 killed<sup id="cite_ref-whiteeagle_9-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-whiteeagle-9"><span>[</span>8<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-Karpus_zwyciezcy_10-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Karpus_zwyciezcy-10"><span>[</span>9<span>]</span></a></sup><br />
113,518 wounded<sup id="cite_ref-Karpus_zwyciezcy_10-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Karpus_zwyciezcy-10"><span>[</span>9<span>]</span></a></sup><br />
51,351 taken prisoner<sup id="cite_ref-Karpus_zwyciezcy_10-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Karpus_zwyciezcy-10"><span>[</span>9<span>]</span></a></sup><br />
