<li>Sławomir Majman, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.warsawvoice.pl/archiwum.phtml/12706/">War and Propaganda</a>, <a href="Warsaw_Voice" title="Warsaw Voice" class="mw-redirect">Warsaw Voice</a>, 23 August 1998</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.york.cuny.edu/~drobnick/russo.html">The Russo-Polish War, 1919–1920: A Bibliography of Materials in English</a> by John A. Drobnicki. Originally Published in the Polish Review, XLII, no. 1 (Mar. 1997), 95–104</li>
</ul>
